I need to transition issues "behind the scenes" and I want notifications to be optional (similar to the option in "Bulk edit"). I'm using the *issueService.transition()* function since that is now the recommended way but there is no way of suppressing the notifications without adding the *sendBulkNotification* parameter in a "hacky" sort of way!

This example works now but I would like a proper API solution:
{code}
IssueService.TransitionValidationResult transitionValidationResult = issueService.validateTransition(...);
transitionValidationResult.getAdditionInputs().put("sendBulkNotification", false);
IssueService.IssueResult transitionResult = issueService.transition(user, transitionValidationResult);
{code}

Many thanks,

Bjarni

P.S. See here for discussion on Answers: https://answers.atlassian.com/questions/40777/transition-issue-without-notification

